name: Harley Quinn (New Style) LoRA [76MB]
description:
I made a Harley Quinn LoRA because I thought that it was a crime that there weren't any uploaded here yet.

Trained on Anything 4, works on other models fine. Most of my best gens were on a walnut merge with the darkness model (first 2 image refs).

You can prompt it however you want, but if you use my provided tags it should be a fairly consistent look.

She does try her hardest to hold a baseball bat since that was present a lot in the dataset, however its nothing you cannot prompt around or use controlnet to subdue.


If you have any LoRA requests and wouldnt mind buying me a Hot Chocolate, please consider going to my page. https://www.buymeacoffee.com/JohnStinko
